{"tid":2495144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳57歲婦商場遭非禮　警擒27歲色狼","createTime":"2021-04-19T04:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T04:33:43.000Z","uid":222155,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd60c70ae895cace2fa8508e20a84f5d9b4742c2","tid":2495144,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"警方上周四(15日)接獲一名57歲女子報案，指她在將軍澳唐賢街一商場被一名陌生男子非禮。將軍澳警區刑事調查隊跟進案件，今午(18日)在尚德邨展開進一步調查，過程中成功鎖定目標，以涉嫌非禮拘捕一名姓張(27歲)男子，他現正被扣留調查。警方重申，非禮屬嚴重罪行，一經定罪，最高可判監禁10年，市民切勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210418/bkn-20210418213230726-0418_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210418%2Fbkn-20210418213230726-0418_00822_001.html&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=daca2a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210418/bkn-20210418213230726-0418_00822_001.html</a></span>"},{"pid":"025f9cf6c6126605686ef1535e27bc8e6be7766f","tid":2495144,"uid":102949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"咁重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb623560334fd02c13cd22b19b65cf65d8111aa","tid":2495144,"uid":147376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVsbU9vhTzD4Qi38t42JQ6HmhHiQ7zM2qwVU6j8W857sb?filename=otLtVJV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotLtVJV.jpg&h=e2d7c7c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"821e298816df5a8d30416ad3a7234e345ce1931a","tid":2495144,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"多圖 會員限定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e963a76c64f1b24a22a03e8e525edc1b6d1c4e","tid":2495144,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT